com.microsoft.bingads.bulk.entities

Class BulkProductAdExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.internal.bulk.entities.MultiRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.bulk.entities.BulkProductAdExtension

  • public class BulkProductAdExtension
extends MultiRecordBulkEntity
    Represents a product ad extension. This class exposes properties that can be read and written as fields of the Product Ad Extension record in a bulk file.

    For more information, see Product Ad Extension at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=511516

    The Product Ad Extension record includes the distinct properties of the BulkProductConditionCollection class, combined with the common properties of the BulkProductAdExtension class, for example AccountId and ProductAdExtension.

    One BulkProductAdExtension has one or more BulkProductConditionCollection. Each BulkProductConditionCollection instance corresponds to one Product Ad Extension record in the bulk file. If you upload a BulkProductAdExtension, then you are effectively replacing any existing product conditions for the product ad extension.

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter

        public List<BulkProductConditionCollection> getProductConditionCollections()
        The list of BulkProductConditionCollection are represented by multiple Product Ad Extension records in the file. Each item in the list corresponds to a separate Product Ad Extension record that includes the distinct properties of the BulkProductConditionCollection class, combined with the common properties of the BulkProductAdExtension class, for example getAccountId() and getProductAdExtension().
